divs: Sighting Detailswe (my dad and I) were headed west on I694 at late dusk and noticed it moving from the south of I694, first east, then north. first cigar-shaped, with white-amber lights, one very bright white (spot)light in center. moved and changed direction very freely-unlike any aircraft we could think of. Ther were a few commercial aircraft in the area, but they were noticed only because the ufo moved so much more quick and agile, which is what finally convinced my dad. would've had much time for photos, but no camera on hand. We lost immediate sight of it as it passed over and behind our view from the car, but then reappeared as a collection of all red lights in a triangular pattern moving to match car speed, then much faster into distance, took a hard left (south) and left from view.
